---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About — Nils Hillmann · dfir.89deg.com">

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="about-hero container">
    <p class="kicker">// ABOUT — FOR THE PERSON DOING THE HIRING</p>
    <h1>Live, laugh, inspect every device I can find.</h1>
    <div class="hero-row">
      <p class="intro">I’m Nils. Not in DFIR yet — but that’s exactly where I’m headed, and this site is the paper trail. Willing to learn the hard stuff, in public: every lab here is dated and reproducible, and the write-ups explain the <em>why</em>, not just the menu clicks.</p>
      <div class="hero-cta">
        <a href="mailto:dfir@89deg.com" class="btn-solid">EMAIL ME →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- AT A GLANCE -->
  <section class="container glance-section">
    <div class="glance">
      <div class="glance-cell">
        <span class="glance-label">LOOKING FOR</span>
        <span class="glance-value">Junior DFIR / SOC Analyst</span>
      </div>
      <div class="glance-cell">
        <span class="glance-label">LOCATION</span>
        <span class="glance-value">Bremen &amp; Niedersachsen</span>
      </div>
      <div class="glance-cell">
        <span class="glance-label">LANGUAGES</span>
        <span class="glance-value">German (native) · English (fluent)</span>
      </div>
      <div class="glance-cell">
        <span class="glance-label">AVAILABILITY</span>
        <span class="glance-value">Immediately</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- STORY + VERIFY -->
  <section class="container story-section">
    <div class="story">
      <h2 class="section-title">WHY FORENSICS</h2>
      <p>For over ten years I’ve been doing quality assurance for mobile apps. Then one day I stumbled across a DFIR job posting, sadly in a city far away, and caught myself wondering what that even was. I fell in love instantly and couldn’t get enough: Windows registry hives, Android live data, how cryptography actually works.</p>
      <p>When I noticed I was spending my free evenings watching Volatility 3 tutorials on YouTube and webinars from the Magnet Virtual Summit, I knew: this is my dream job. Now I use the small time slots I have — between a full-time job and two kids — to learn and get things done. I share my achievements here, so maybe someone who shares the same interest and is willing to learn will find them.</p>
      <p>If you’re searching for a junior DFIR or SOC analyst — public service or private sector — I’d appreciate <a href="mailto:dfir@89deg.com">hearing from you</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="container cta-section">
    <div class="cta-box">
      <div class="cta-copy">
        <h2>The fastest way to evaluate me is a conversation.</h2>
        <p>Send a mail, get an answer within 24 hours. Pick any artifact on this site and I'll walk you through how I got there.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="cta-buttons">
        <a href="mailto:dfir@89deg.com" class="cta-mail">dfir@89deg.com</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-hero {
    padding-top: 72px;
  }
  h1 {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: clamp(34px, 7.5vw, 56px);
    line-height: 1.08;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: -0.015em;
    max-width: 20ch;
    text-wrap: balance;
  }
  .hero-row {
    margin-top: 26px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 620px) 1fr;
    gap: 72px;
    align-items: end;
  }
  .intro {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 20px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--dim);
    text-wrap: pretty;
  }
  .hero-cta { display: flex; justify-content: flex-end; }
  .hero-cta .btn-solid { white-space: nowrap; padding: 14px 24px; }
  .glance-section { padding-top: 56px; }
  .glance {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--ink);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--hairline);
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
  }
  .glance-cell {
    padding: 22px 24px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 6px;
    border-right: 1px solid var(--hairline);
  }
  .glance-cell:first-child { padding-left: 0; }
  .glance-cell:last-child { padding-right: 0; border-right: none; }
  .glance-label {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10.5px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--faint);
  }
  .glance-value { font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.4; }

  .story-section { padding-top: 64px; }
  .story { max-width: 660px; }
  .section-title {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--ink);
    padding-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .story p {
    margin: 24px 0 0 0;
    font-size: 18.5px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--body);
    text-wrap: pretty;
  }
  .story p + p { margin-top: 18px; }
  .story a {
    color: var(--accent);
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--accent-bd);
  }
  .story a:hover { border-bottom-color: var(--accent); }

  .cta-section { padding-top: 84px; padding-bottom: 84px; }
  .cta-box {
    border: 1px solid var(--ink);
    background: var(--panel-dark);
    color: #E8EBE8;
    padding: 52px 56px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.4fr 1fr;
    gap: 48px;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .cta-copy h2 {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 36px;
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.15;
    max-width: 18ch;
    text-wrap: balance;
  }
  .cta-copy p {
    margin: 16px 0 0 0;
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: #9BA59E;
    max-width: 48ch;
    text-wrap: pretty;
  }
  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 14px;
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 13px;
  }
  .cta-mail {
    background: var(--accent);
    color: #F2F8F4;
    padding: 14px 22px;
    text-align: center;
    text-decoration: none;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }
  .cta-mail:hover { background: #7FC79F; color: #10241A; }
  @media (max-width: 760px) {
    .hero-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; }
    .glance { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    .glance-cell { padding: 16px 16px 16px 0 !important; border-right: none !important; }
    .glance-cell:nth-child(-n+2) { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--hairline); }
    .cta-box { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 24px; padding: 32px 24px; }
  }
</style>
